## 1. Automation Pipeline — Plan & Costs Analysis

User asked about costs in `docs/automation-outreach-plan.md`.
- Only paid cost: Google Places API ~$17/1000 firms
- Everything else: free tiers

User asked for free alternatives → decided to use:
- **OpenStreetMap Overpass API** (free, unlimited) as primary
- **Yelp Fusion API** (free 5000 calls/day) for ratings
- **Panorama Firm scraping** for Polish directory
- Google Places API deferred until business validates

Plan updated in `docs/automation-outreach-plan.md`.

