## 4. Booking System — tasks3.md Group 1 Implementation

### Existing booking system (before changes):
- DB: `bookings` table with confirmToken/cancelToken fields (unused)
- API: `/api/booking/[businessId]/availability` (GET) + `/api/booking/[businessId]/reserve` (POST)
- Admin: `/api/admin/bookings/list` + `/api/admin/bookings/update-status`
- UI: BookingWidget.tsx (4-step: service → datetime → customer → success)
- No emails, no SMS, no reminders, no cancellation UI

### Files created:
- `apps/engine/src/lib/booking-emails.ts` — 3 email functions:
  - `sendBookingConfirmationEmail()` — to customer with details + cancel link
  - `sendBookingNotificationToOwner()` — to business owner with customer info
  - `sendBookingReminderEmail()` — reminder with configurable label ("jutro"/"za godzinę")

- `apps/engine/src/pages/api/booking/cancel.ts` — GET endpoint
  - Validates cancel token, updates status to "cancelled"
  - Returns styled HTML confirmation page
  - Handles edge cases (already cancelled, completed)

- `apps/engine/src/pages/api/booking/reminders.ts` — GET cron endpoint
  - Auth via `?secret=CRON_SECRET`
  - 24h reminders: queries confirmed bookings for tomorrow → sends email
  - 1h reminders: queries confirmed bookings in next hour → sends SMS
  - Returns count of sent emails/SMS

### Files modified:
- `apps/engine/src/pages/api/booking/[businessId]/reserve.ts`:
  - Generates confirmToken + cancelToken (crypto.randomBytes)
  - Sends confirmation email to customer + notification to owner (non-blocking)
  - Sends SMS confirmation if sms notifications enabled

- `apps/engine/src/pages/api/booking/[businessId]/availability.ts`:
  - Added blackout dates check (`blackoutDates` array in config)
  - Replaced simple `bookedTimes` Set with overlap-based range checking including buffer
  - `bufferMinutes` creates blocked ranges around existing bookings

- `packages/schema/src/business.schema.json`:
  - Added `bufferMinutes` (integer, default 0) to booking config
  - Added `blackoutDates` (string array) to booking config

- `packages/db/src/queries.ts` — 3 new functions:
  - `getBookingByCancelToken(token)` → Booking | null
  - `getBookingByConfirmToken(token)` → Booking | null
  - `getUpcomingBookings(date, startTime, endTime)` → Booking[]

- `packages/db/src/index.ts` — exported new query functions

### Commit:
`598978a` — feat: booking confirmations, reminders, cancellation, buffer time, blackout dates

